ᴅs ᴡɪᴛʜ ɴᴏ ʜᴏᴍᴇ ᴛʀᴀɪɴɪɴɢ:</h4><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2883ef70-8275-4840-b28c-03c272011aa3_character-lucky-peirce\" target=\"_blank\">ʟᴜᴄᴋʏ</a>,<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a63d6f21-01ee-4470-bb97-245df0456320_character-maison-woods\" target=\"_blank\">ᴍᴀɪsᴏɴ</a>, <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b7e0c81c-baa2-409e-9752-ce68cb0ea99d_character-lucien-aston\" target=\"_blank\">ʟᴜᴄɪᴇɴ</a>, <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/06769dc7-50f2-478c-b59a-a562cf6b0ba6_character-josiah\" target=\"_blank\">ᴊᴏsɪᴀʜ</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"878107f6-c7af-40ca-9ab8-9bf06d25b700_4a9a81f0-90cd-495c-b06a-909637ffadf7.webp","creator":"GMOGHOST","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👩 FemPov"],"chats":1024,"messages":36534,"created_at":"2024-06-07T15:42:07.739352+00:00"}